abstract: Israeli officials announce that diplomatic office will be opened in United Arab Emirates, first time Israel will have official presence in Persian Gulf in over decade.
lead_paragraph: The mission at the International Renewable Energy Agency will be the first time in more than a decade that there will be an official Israeli presence in the Persian Gulf.

headline.main: Israel to Open Diplomatic Office in United Arab Emirates
headline.print_headline: Israel to Establish Office in United Arab Emirates
